section#sobre.container.section.screen-page.reveal
  .section-head
    div
      h2.about-title.section-title
        span.title-word Sobre
        span.title-word.title-word-accent Nós
      .history-page-line.section-title-line(aria-hidden='true')

  .card-grid.about-grid
    a.glass-card.about-card.about-from-left.tilted-card(href='#historia')
      span.about-card-icon(aria-hidden='true')
        svg(viewBox='0 0 24 24' role='presentation' focusable='false')
          path(d='M5 4.5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h12v17H7a2 2 0 0 0-2 2z')
          path(d='M7 2.5v17')
          path(d='M10 7.5h6')
          path(d='M10 11h6')
      span.tilted-card-content
        h3.about-card-title A Nossa História
        p Conhece o percurso da AEEUM e os marcos dos últimos anos.

    a.glass-card.about-card.about-from-top.tilted-card(href='#departamentos')
      span.about-card-icon(aria-hidden='true')
        svg(viewBox='0 0 24 24' role='presentation' focusable='false')
          path(d='M16 19v-1.2a3.8 3.8 0 0 0-3.8-3.8H7.8A3.8 3.8 0 0 0 4 17.8V19')
          circle(cx='10' cy='8' r='3')
          path(d='M20 19v-1a3 3 0 0 0-2.2-2.9')
          path(d='M15.8 5.2a3 3 0 0 1 0 5.6')
      span.tilted-card-content
        h3.about-card-title.about-card-title-nowrap A&nbsp;Nossa&nbsp;Equipa
        p Descobre a estrutura atual da direção e os departamentos que a compõem.

    a.glass-card.about-card.about-from-left.tilted-card(href='#atividades')
      span.about-card-icon(aria-hidden='true')
        svg(viewBox='0 0 24 24' role='presentation' focusable='false')
          rect(x='3.5' y='5.5' width='17' height='15' rx='2')
          path(d='M3.5 10h17')
          path(d='M8 3.5v4')
          path(d='M16 3.5v4')
          path(d='M8.5 14h3')
      span.tilted-card-content
        h3.about-card-title Atividades
        p Vê os eventos, projetos e iniciativas em destaque no calendário.

    a.glass-card.about-card.about-from-bottom.tilted-card(href='#documentos')
      span.about-card-icon(aria-hidden='true')
        svg(viewBox='0 0 24 24' role='presentation' focusable='false')
          path(d='M7 3.5h7l4 4V20.5H7z')
          path(d='M14 3.5v4h4')
          path(d='M9.5 12h5')
          path(d='M9.5 15.5h5')
      span.tilted-card-content
        h3.about-card-title Documentos
        p Acede a estatutos, atas, planos e documentação institucional.

    a.glass-card.about-card.about-from-right.tilted-card(href='#antigos-presidentes')
      span.about-card-icon(aria-hidden='true')
        svg(viewBox='0 0 24 24' role='presentation' focusable='false')
          path(d='M7.5 5.5h9v4.5a4.5 4.5 0 0 1-9 0z')
          path(d='M7.5 7.2H6a2 2 0 0 0 0 4h1.2')
          path(d='M16.5 7.2H18a2 2 0 0 1 0 4h-1.2')
          path(d='M12 14.5v3')
          path(d='M9 20.5h6')
      span.tilted-card-content
        h3.about-card-title Antigos Presidentes
        p Consulta os mandatos anteriores e quem liderou a associação.
